metadata.name: FOK witlinkAI GO WOMLand
metadata.description:
Witlink and MetaGems Genesis exclusive Land. This NFT will represent a parcel of land on a private island we will create exclusively for the persons who got rugged by WitlinkAI and the holders of our Genesis collection.

This island will be accessible at the launch of our beta version on the Ethereum mainnet. The beta version of our metaverse will be available in early 2023  Important: Nor a MetaGems Genesis NFT or a worthless WitlinkAI Land will be needed to build on this Land plot. It will be usable by anyone like all the other World of MetaGems types of Land.
